      <title>犯罪和腐败使南非的标准普尔评级受到控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/crime-corruption-keep-south-africa-s-s-p-rating-in-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级表示，正在密切关注南非下周的选举结果以及随后的政府政策，以解决从犯罪到能源供应等阻碍投资的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/crime-corruption-keep-south-africa-s-s-p-rating-in-check</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班称匈牙利正努力“重新定义”其北约成员国身份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/hungary-working-to-redefine-its-nato-membership-orban-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克托表示，匈牙利正在努力“重新定义”该国的北约成员国地位，以便在军事联盟在其领土之外采取军事行动时允许选择退出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/hungary-working-to-redefine-its-nato-membership-orban-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 06:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 7 月份大选前能源账单将下降 7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/uk-energy-bills-to-drop-7-in-july-ahead-of-general-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国家庭能源费用将于 7 月份下降，同周该国将进行选举投票，生活成本是一个关键问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/uk-energy-bills-to-drop-7-in-july-ahead-of-general-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 06:03:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
